Package: icd10am.elixhauser
Title: Elixhauser Comorbidity Index for ICD-10-AM Coded Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jim", "Pearse", email = "ejpearse@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Applies the Elixhauser Comorbidity Index to Australian admitted patient care data coded using ICD-10-AM. Supports both wide and long input formats and returns van Walraven weighted scores.
